snippet.textDisplay: Wondering how Momina got 3 consecutive songs in a single season?? and Rachael Viccaji who is singing for so many years in Coke Studio is not getting a chance to sing as a lead singer?? Guys Momina's father is an Army General. I am not showing my hate or anything like that. I love Pak Army especially COAS Raheel Sharif. But let's be honest for a moment, we all know the power of Generals. It hurts me to see that a superior singer (Rachael) is always singing as a background singer and Momina just came and got 3 songs for nothing. What I am simply trying to say is that Rachael has got more experience, more talent, better voice, and yet she is always kept as a background singer. WHY???
